snippet.title: Midtown Madness 3 Intro
snippet.description:
Hello, YouTubers! Welcome to my first video and my new channel on YouTube!

Channel link:
http://www.youtube.com/user/CEO100able 

I have downloaded this video from a website, though I forgot what the site name is. This is my first video and even my first Midtown Madness 3 video to be on YouTube. I do not own this piece of game content; Microsoft does. Please comment and subscribe.
